items.sentence: Tom doesn't seem to be as successful as Mary.
Tom didn't stop singing when we asked him to.
Tom claimed he shot the Mary in self-defense.
Tom can't find a babysitter for Monday night.
Tom asked his boss if he could go home early.
Tom asked Mary to visit John in the hospital.
Tom asked Mary if he could watch TV with her.
Tom and Mary are coming to visit us tomorrow.
Tom and I were the only ones who were hungry.
Since both Tom and I were sick, we didn't go.
